  "text": "Because our interests were to use cytokines as adjuvants in nonhuman primates, we first attempted to clone and sequence the nonhuman primate homologs of human cytokines and since, then have also cloned and sequenced a variety of other immunologically relevant nonhuman primate molecules [CITATION_1] (5) [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
